---

<section id="ctasection" class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    
    <span class="eyebrow">PRÓXIMO PASSO</span>
    
    <h2 class="title">
      <span class="title-intro">Você já esperou tempo demais.</span><br />
      A SUA DOR NO OMBRO <span class="glow-text">TEM SOLUÇÃO</span>.
    </h2>
    
    <p class="subtitle">
      Em uma única consulta, você terá diagnóstico claro e plano de tratamento para sua dor<br />
    </p>

    <a href="https://wa.me/5541999782006?text=Ol%C3%A1!%20Gostaria%20de%20marcar%20uma%20consulta%20com%20o%20Dr.%20Luiz%20com%20rela%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20a%20meu%20ombro" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta-button">
      <svg class="btn-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512" fill="#ffffff">
        <path d="M380.9 97.1C339 55.1 283.2 32 223.9 32c-122.4 0-222 99.6-222 222 0 39.1 10.2 77.3 29.6 111L0 480l117.7-30.9c32.4 17.7 68.9 27 106.1 27h.1c122.3 0 224.1-99.6 224.1-222 0-59.3-25.2-115-67.1-157.1zm-157 341.6c-33.2 0-65.7-8.9-94-25.7l-6.7-4-69.8 18.3L72 359.2l-4.4-7c-18.5-29.4-28.2-63.3-28.2-98.2 0-101.7 82.8-184.5 184.6-184.5 49.3 0 95.6 19.2 130.4 54.1 34.8 34.9 56.2 81.2 56.1 130.5 0 101.8-84.9 184.6-186.6 184.6zm101.2-138.2c-5.5-2.8-32.8-16.2-37.9-18-5.1-1.9-8.8-2.8-12.5 2.8-3.7 5.6-14.3 18-17.6 21.8-3.2 3.7-6.5 4.2-12 1.4-32.6-16.3-54-29.1-75.5-66-5.7-9.8 5.7-9.1 16.3-30.3 1.8-3.7.9-6.9-.5-9.7-1.4-2.8-12.5-30.1-17.1-41.2-4.5-10.8-9.1-9.3-12.5-9.5-3.2-.2-6.9-.2-10.6-.2-3.7 0-9.7 1.4-14.8 6.9-5.1 5.6-19.4 19-19.4 46.3 0 27.3 19.9 53.7 22.6 57.4 2.8 3.7 39.1 59.7 94.8 83.8 35.2 15.2 49 16.5 66.6 13.9 10.7-1.6 32.8-13.4 37.4-26.4 4.6-13 4.6-24.1 3.2-26.4-1.3-2.5-5-3.9-10.5-6.6z"/>
      </svg>
      Agendar Minha Consulta pelo WhatsApp
    </a>

    <div class="features-list">
      <div class="feature-item">
        <svg class="feature-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path></svg>
        Atendimento humanizado
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <svg class="feature-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"></path></svg>
        Consulta particular
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <svg class="feature-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle></svg>
        Curitiba · PR
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-section {
    background-color: #0d2220; /* Fundo verde super escuro, quase preto */
    padding: 8rem 1rem 9rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: #f69f46; /* Laranja/Dourado */
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .glow-text {
    color: #ffffff;
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(23, 164, 136, 0.8),
                 0 0 40px rgba(23, 164, 136, 0.6),
                 0 0 60px rgba(23, 164, 136, 0.4);
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: #aebec2;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 3rem 0;
  }

  .margin-top-small {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* Estilos do Badge de Agendamento */
  .availability-badge {
    border: 1px solid #4a4224; /* Borda puxada pro dourado escuro */
    background-color: rgba(246, 159, 70, 0.05);
    color: #f69f46;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background-color: #f69f46;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: inline-block;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(246, 159, 70, 0.6);
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0% { transform: scale(0.95); box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(246, 159, 70, 0.7); }
    70% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(246, 159, 70, 0); }
    100% { transform: scale(0.95); box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(246, 159, 70, 0); }
  }

  /* Botão CTA Principal */
  .cta-button {
    background-color: #17a488; /* Verde vibrante do print */
    color: #ffffff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(23, 164, 136, 0.3);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background-color: #148f76;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .btn-icon {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
  }

  /* Lista de Benefícios do Rodapé */
  .features-list {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
    color: #6a8280; /* Texto discreto */
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    color: #f69f46; /* Ícones em laranja/dourado */
  }

  /* Responsividade */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cta-section {
      padding: 5rem 1rem 4rem 1rem;
    }

    .title-intro {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      opacity: 0.8;
      margin-bottom: -1.7rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    
    .subtitle br {
      display: none;
    }

    .cta-button {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .availability-badge {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .features-list {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
